title: Rock Ola
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This little cafe has an entire vegan menu separate from the regular menu. Includes 3 vegan breakfast items, burger, hot dog, southern fried chicken, falafel wrap, chilli wrap, a vegan chocolate milkshake, and vegan flapjack. American diner decor with rock theme and free jukebox.
